Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想大鬧一場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真挺疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我的集章手冊被捅了個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣危險的事情還是少做吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總算是避免了觀眾們的恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
